value: Breeds locally in Europe and Asia from central Sweden, Gulf of Bothnia, Ladoga Lake, Arkhangelsk, lat. 66Â° 35' N. on the Ob, 64Â° on the Lena, and shores of the Sea of Okhotsk, south to Denmark, East Prussia, central Russia (gouvernements of Smolensk, Moscow, Kazan and Ufa), steppes of western Siberia, the Altai, and Lake Baikal.
